<h2><span id="2._c4_-_R.C3.A9ti_Opening"></span><span id="2._c4_-_Réti_Opening">2. c4 - Réti Opening</span></h2>
<p>The Réti Opening is a hypermodern chess opening. White plans to bring the d5-pawn under attack from the flank, or entice it to advance to d4 and undermine it later. White will couple this plan with a Kingside fianchetto (g3 and Bg2) to create pressure on the light squares in the center.
</p>
